      "sc:description": "Imagetwin is an AI-powered image analysis tool that detects integrity issues like duplication, manipulation, and AI-generated content in research papers. The American Society for Microbiology (ASM) has integrated Imagetwin into its editorial workflow to enhance research integrity.",
